title: Looking for dedicated members of , "The Moose Order" Ranked 5v5 team (any rank, Non Toxic)
body: I play Top lane mostly but am fine in other lanes, I am in need of all the other roles, ADC, JG, Support and Mid laners to join "The Moose Order" led by me IGN: SlipperyMoose96. doesnt matter the rank considering I myself am currently Bronze 3 and trying to climb. we are going to hopefully grow together as a team and get better as time goes on. If this is something that would interest you then pls let me know. I run on New Zealand hours and am online most evenings to play games and most of weekends. I will also consider adding some filler people for when others are offline. (please for the love of god no toxic people who get angry with losing. I want a safe environment) I will be back today to play at about 1:30pm NZ time (like 2 hours from this post) so add me and request to join
